body:
Finally, at Home…

She can feel herself the very moment her concise return, she feel relax, feel alive despite saying good bye to clint only few moments ago.

She try to open her eyes as slowly as she could there were not so much light but just the amount you can see clearly in, she slowly rise from surface where she was laying, it was soft but there were not any bed nor any soft object to provide her comfort.

She look around after finally rising to her feet there was no one in sight for second as she look here and there and suddenly she can see some people standing not far away from her.

A woman with build somehow similar to her own with those green eyes, but at same moment she had a smile on her face that was similar to her own, an expression only reserved for her family, for avengers. Beside her a man stood there with woman’s hand in his, he look taller but had same red hair, so natural. There was also little figure she cant see it enough to determine its feature but know that it was girl no more than 4 or 5 years old.

Natasha had not seen them in her life but somehow they seems familiar, it feels like she know them all along.

“who are you?,” Natasha asked walking slowly towards them, “what place is this?” she question again.

“hello любить,” comes the woman’s answer as she held her hand for her to grasp, beckoning her to come forward.

Natasha know the moment the words left from woman mouth that who they were, and she cant help as a lone tear slip down her own chick.

“You can finally rest now my милая” this time the words come from man as he also smile at her, and offer her his hand.

Natasha walk towards them with his own watery smile and she know she can rest now. She had finally found where she belong, at home with her family.

——*——*——-*——-*——*——

Something about Natasha finally finding her family, her peace as she sacrifice her life for her loved ones, for avengers.
